#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Desktop Session"
msgstr "Seja namizja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this &systemsettings; module you can configure &plasma;'s session manager "
"and logout settings."
msgstr ""
"V tem modulu &systemsettings; lahko konfigurirate nastavitve upravitelja sej "
"in odjave v &plasma;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Session management refers to &plasma;'s ability to save the state of "
"applications and windows when you log out of &plasma; and restore them when "
"you log back in."
msgstr ""
"Upravljanje sej se navezuje na sposobnost programa &plasma;, da shrani "
"stanje aplikacij in oken, ko se odjavite iz programa &plasma;, in jih "
"obnovi, ko se ponovno prijavite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ask for confirmation: on shutdown, restart, and logout"
msgstr "Vprašaj za potrditev: ob izklopu, ponovnem zagonu in odjavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this setting is turned on, the logout confirmation screen will be shown "
"when you log out, shut down, or restart. When the setting is turned off, "
"your computer will log out, shut down, etc. immediately after clicking the "
"respective button."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta nastavitev vklopljena, bo prikazan zaslon za potrditev, ko se "
"odjavite, izklopite ali znova zaženete. Ko je nastavitev izklopljena, se bo "
"vaš računalnik takoj po kliku ustreznega gumba odjavil, zaustavil itd."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "On login, launch apps that were open"
msgstr "Ob prijavi zaženi aplikacije, ki so bile odprte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may choose one of three options on what should happen when you log into "
"&plasma;:"
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko eno od treh možnosti, kaj naj se zgodi, ko se prijavite v "
"&plasma;:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "On last logout"
msgstr "Ob zadnji prijavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, &plasma; will save your current session's state "
"when you logout. &plasma; will restore your session on the next login, so "
"you can continue to work with a desktop just like you left it."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo &plasma; ob odjavi shranila stanje trenutne "
"seje. &plasma; bo ob naslednji prijavi obnovila sejo, tako da boste lahko "
"nadaljevali delo z namizjem, kot ste ga zapustili."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "When session was manually saved"
msgstr "Ko je bila seja shranjena ročno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instead of restoring &plasma; to the state it was when you logged out last, "
"it will be restored to a specific state that you have saved manually."
msgstr ""
"Namesto da bi se obnovilo stanje &plasma;, ki je bilo ob zadnji odjavi, se "
"obnovi določeno stanje, ki ste ga shranili ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <guilabel>Save Session</guilabel> button will appear in the "
"<guilabel>Application Launcher</guilabel> menu and &plasma; search. When you "
"click it, &plasma; will remember the apps that are open and restore them on "
"the next login. Click it again to replace the set of remembered apps."
msgstr ""
"V meniju <guilabel>Zaganjalnik aplikacij</guilabel> in &plasma; iskanju se "
"pojavi gumb <guilabel>Shrani sejo</guilabel>. Ko ga kliknete, si &plasma; "
"zapomni odprte aplikacije in jih obnovi ob naslednji prijavi. Ponovno ga "
"kliknite, da zamenjate nabor zapomnjenih aplikacij."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start with an empty session"
msgstr "Začni s prazno sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose this option, &plasma; will never restore sessions that it has "
"saved."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, program &plasma; ne bo nikoli obnovil shranjenih sej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, you can enter a colon (<literal>:</literal>) or comma (<literal>,</"
"literal>) separated list of applications that should be excluded from "
"sessions, and therefore will not be started when restoring a session. For "
"example <userinput>xterm:konsole</userinput> or <userinput>xterm,konsole</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje lahko vnesete z dvopičjem (<literal>:</literal>) ali vejico "
"(<literal>,</literal>) ločen seznam aplikacij, ki jih je treba izključiti iz "
"sej in se zato pri obnovitvi seje ne bodo zagnali. Na primer "
"<userinput>xterm:konsole</userinput> ali <userinput>xterm,konsole</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Firmware"
msgstr "Programska oprema"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "After next restart: Enter UEFI setup screen"
msgstr "Po naslednjem ponovnem zagonu: Vstopite v zaslon za nastavitev UEFI"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, the next time you restart your computer, it will "
"enter the firmware setup mode (BIOS/UEFI). This may be easier than trying to "
"enter the firmware setup by quickly pressing special keys during boot."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, bo računalnik ob naslednjem ponovnem zagonu "
"vstopil v način nastavitve vdelane programske opreme (BIOS/UEFI). To je "
"morda lažje, kot če bi poskušali vstopiti v nastavitve vdelane programske "
"opreme s hitrim pritiskanjem posebnih tipk med zagonom."

